quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  4,97,"Ih, i wid iwumi ddment lmalayek leôwaê, u densen iman nnsen, ad inint: \"anida tellam\"? A d inin: \"nella d uôhifen di tmurt\". Ad inint: \"day ur tewsiâ ara tmurt n Öebbi, a ppinigem degs\"? Widak, axxam nnsen d Loahennama. A tu$alin tucmip"
  4,98,"Kkes ed uôhifen, argaz, tameîîut, agrud, ur nezmir i tsensert, ur nepwanhu s abrid"
  4,99,"Widak, amar Öebbi ad asen Isemmeê. Öebbi Izga Ipqili, Ipsemmiê"
  4,100,"Win iunagen deg ubrid n Öebbi, ad iaf, di tmurt, aîas n ssôanat akked lufa. Win iff$en seg uxxam is, d iminig ar Öebbi akked Umazan iS, sinna, temmuger it tmeppant, arraz is atan ar Öebbi. Öebbi Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"